name: The Daily Chronicles of Cindy Tran
name_original: The Daily Chronicles of Cindy Tran
description:
Follow the life of cindy tran as she navigates her life through school, work, and friends/family!!!

My game is about a day in a life as me!!! It is important to me because it talks about my life as a college student and I think my game is significant because every single college student should be able to relate to this game and have fun with it. The game would also encourage people (like me cough cough) that no matter how good or bad your day is, life can always get better!
